data.description: Discover modern comfort in this spacious 3-bedroom condo with 1 1/2 Baths, now available for sale. This well-maintained unit features a newer roof and fence, ensuring peace of mind and low maintenance. With three levels of living space, including a finished basement, an open-concept kitchen, and a versatile bonus room, there's plenty of room to spread out and make it your own. Additionally, the single-car garage provides convenient parking and storage options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this condo your new home sweet home.Come join us on 12/16 from 12-2pm for our Open House!
